{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"文化大革命十年颂歌——少数民族新民歌选","authors":["李耀宗"],"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":5,"day":16}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命十年颂歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——少数民族新民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓦吉瓦，文化大革命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔彝族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十九朵彩云啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知能纺多少线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十九座松林啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知长有多少针；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十九张月琴啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知装着多少歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九十九个寨子啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知欢跳着多少心……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云遮不住金色的线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨打不落金色的针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山隔不断金色的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风吹不动革命的心——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年啊，日夜飞向金水桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年啊，日夜绣织幸福锦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福锦永开幸福花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓦吉瓦，文化大革命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　瓦吉瓦：彝语，好得很。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开十年遍全国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔羌族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命浪淘沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪头开出革命花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开十年遍全国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万人心中把根扎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平想把花儿砍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民要斗倒他！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学鲲鹏万里程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔撒拉族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山丹花根是一蔸根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金根根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒拉族人民一条心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗红心亮晶晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年文化大革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马莲花呀，是乱根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑又深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平翻案是狼心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒拉族人民反复辟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旌旗奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学那鲲鹏万里程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布朗人民反复辟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔布朗族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙蜂的蜇刺最毒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断了还想蜇树皮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鹰的爪子最狠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死了还想抓山鸡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资派不肯改悔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做梦都想搞复辟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南开河水向前淌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞滩穿岩不停息；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄树干向阳长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打不偏移；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布朗人民心向党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远革命反复辟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命通天流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔畲族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命通天流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年万代流不休，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流不休；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资派翻案要逆流走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们叫他淹没浪里头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金笛声声拨心弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔苗族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京春风到苗山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青青竹笋冒银尖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年文化大革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山新竹刺云天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根金竹一管笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金笛声声拨心弦："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命就是好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新生事物红万年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞歌响心弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔鄂温克族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉河鱼鳞般的银波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有夏秋能带来温暖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄂温克草原的绿浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有春天招牛羊撒欢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命的赞歌啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季拨响我们心弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色大路长又长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔纳西族新民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在高高玉龙山深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年来铺出一条路；路通北京连全国啊，灿烂鲜花路上铺。纳西跨上这条路，心中闪现万里长征图；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色大路长又长啊，世代向前不停步！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔李耀宗整理〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}